history.content:
EDIT: Our application is now open until Wednesday night! You can apply even if you did not attend the info session.

Hey everyone! The iOS DeCal will be offered this Fall. If you've taken CS 61A/B or equivalent and want to learn Swift and iOS fundamentals, this course if for you! Class will be MW, 7-8 PM starting 9/3.

We're hosting an info session for those interested in applying today, 8/27 7-8 PM in Moffitt 145. We'll be discussing more about the course and its requirements there!

Check out our DeCal page, visit the course website (to be updated), or email iosdecalstaff@gmail.com for more information on the class.
